**Usage:** Very low opacity (8–12%) background texture behind the simulation title area

### Image 2 — Artifact Icon (Spectrum Navigator)
**Prompt:** "Compass rose icon where north and south points are colored purple and teal respectively, east and west points are amber gold, the compass center contains a sacred geometry mandala pattern, dark background, glowing subtle lines, suitable as a small square icon, 1:1 aspect ratio, symbolic and elegant"

**Usage:** The artifact card icon (displayed at approximately 64×64px)

---

## 15. COMPONENT BOUNDARIES

**This component does NOT include:**
- The intro description paragraph (that lives in Framer above the embedded component)
- The Quiz that follows (that is a separate component in the method chain)
- Any progress bar or lesson completion tracking (handled by Framer/Outsetta)

**This component DOES include:**
- All slider logic and visual states
- All six attribute cards with tooltips
- Shared Territory column with tooltips
- All three Discovery Moments
- Artifact unlock sequence and animation
- Exploration Prompt column with state transitions
- Responsive layout handling
- Local state tracking for artifact unlock conditions

